extends layout

block content
  h1 Internships / Become an Intern
  p.lead Instructions on how to apply for internship, the information needed, personal info. Maybe make a virtual checklist?
  p We require that you submit the following information to be considered for an internship
  p Require login to apply? That seems to be normal. Maybe fill in from LinkedIn, Facebook, etc.
  p Add in the paperwork here?
  hr

  page-header
    h3.text-center Please fill out the fields, below.

  form.form-horizontal(method='POST')
    input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
    .form-group
      label(class='col-sm-2 control-label', for='name') Your Full Name
      .col-sm-8
        input.form-control(type='text', name='name', id='name', autofocus=true)
    .form-group
      label(class='col-sm-2 control-label', for='email') Your Email
      .col-sm-8
        input.form-control(type='text', name='email', id='email')
    .form-group
      label(class='col-sm-2 control-label', for='message') Body
      .col-sm-8
        textarea.form-control(name='message', id='message', rows='7')
    .form-group
      .col-sm-offset-2.col-sm-8
        | Add reCaptcha checkbox from Google here
        br
        button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit')
          i.fa.fa-envelope
          | Send